    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The checksums are the ones the Azure blobstore provides. They only support MD5, hence why we added it as a sanity check. If you want to make sure the file has not been tampered with, I'd advise to verify the attached signatures instead of relying on checksums.",
